*******************************************************************************************************************
	BLOCKS
*******************************************************************************************************************
*******************************************************************************************************************


<block intro>
/ trials = [
	1 = intro; 
	2 = demoRespond; 
	3-12 = noreplace(demoRespond, demoWait);
]
</block>

Note: 
