* followed by a random order of 153 GO trials and 80 Nogo_SL trials (that are followed by 80 GO_SL trials)
=> 314 trials
<block SL>
/onblockbegin = [
	values.blocktype = "SL";
	values.countSLblocks += 1;
]
/trials = [
	1 = SL; 
	2 = startGo; 
	3-235 = noreplace (
